<html lang="en">
    <head>
        {% include '../components/global_head.njk' %}
    </head>
    <body>
        {% include '../components/nav.njk' %}
        <div id="wrap">
            {# Content minimum height wrapper, place between nav and footer #}
            <div class='hero-with-cta splash-big'>
                {# Hero banner #}
                <div class="img-container">
                    <div class="dynamic-splash" style="background-image: url('/images/Simplify-Systems-Splash.png')">
                        <h1 style="line-height: 1.1; color: #43c7f4; margin-block-start: 0; margin-block-end: 0;">
                    Let's face it,<br>you need better<br>systems.
                    </h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='hero-cta'>
                    {# Hero Call to Action #}
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-product-overview skeleton block-full' >
                {# Product Overview #}
                <div class="flex-container" id="flexible-tech-consulting" style=" padding-inline:20%" >
                    <div class="div-sticky">
                        <div class="text-column-h1">
                            Built for your needs
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style=" width: 50%; padding-left: 10%">
                        <div class="">
                            <h2>Modular</h2>
                            <h5>Replace your entire system or just use Rapid to plug the holes.</h5>
                            <p>We can build projects in modular blocks, so you can see the value we provide, and pay as you go.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Secure</h2>
                            <h5>Worry-free data. Our security-first platform secures your data with the best that Microsoft has to offer.</h5>
                            <p>Hosted in the Azure cloud, get enterprise grade safety without the enterprise grade development costs.</p>
                            <p>Never have to worry about losing data with item level roll-back and full edit history as standard.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Flexible</h2>
                            <h5>Need to wait for approval or sign-off? Your custom solution will be built according to your schedule, not ours.</h5>
                            <p>Our team aren’t called Rapid for nothing. With agile cycles and a focus on immediacy of result, avoid getting trapped in dead ends.</p>
                            <p>How can we build so fast? Check out our <u>Technology</u>.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Responsible</h2>
                            <h5>Technology impacts lives and we’re all in this together.</h5>
                            <p>We empower organisations through technology, but never lose sight of the human element.</p>
                            <p>We support NFPs, like <u>Simpli,</u> and are committed to supporting people trying to improve the world.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Aussie</h2>
                            <h5>Proudly Australian owned &amp; operated, delivering excellence nationwide.</h5>
                            <p>Being an Aussie company means we understand the unique needs and values of the Australian market.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-purpose skeleton block-full'>
                {# Why we exist #}
                <div class="flex-container">
                    <div class="flex-item">
                        <h1 style="line-height: 1.1; color: #43c7f4; margin-block-start: 0; margin-block-end: 0;">
                            <div class="flex-item-title">
                        streamline<br>your<br>business
                    </div>
                        </h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-item">
                        <p>We specialise in <b>streamlining systems</b>, <b>improving processes</b>, and helping companies <b>go paperless</b>.</p>
                        <p>
                            <a href="/technology">Show me some examples</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-benifit skeleton block-full'>
                {# Why you benifit from us #}
                <div class="flex-container">
                    <div class="flex-item">
                        <h1 style="line-height: 1.1; color: #43c7f4; margin-block-start: 0; margin-block-end: 0;">
                            <div class="flex-item-title">
                        rapidly<br>solve your<br>headaches.
                    </div>
                        </h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-item">
                        <p>Your custom solution can be built in <b>weeks, not months.</b> With nearly a <b>decade of industry experience</b>, we're systems experts.</p>
                        <p>
                            <a href="/technology">How do you build so quickly?</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-call-to-action skeleton block-full'>
                {# Main call to action #}
                <div class="img-container">
                    <div class="dynamic-splash" style="background-image: url('/images/Simplify-Systems-CTA.png')">
                        <h1 style="line-height: 1.1; color: #43c7f4; margin-block-start: 0; margin-block-end: 0;">Test</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-justification skeleton block-full'>
                {# Justification why other people think we're great #}
                <!--Testimonials-->
                <div class="testimony-container">
                    <!-- First Testimony -->
                    <div class="flex-item-testimony">
                        <div class="testimony-speaker">
                            <div class="testimonial-head">
                                <img src="/images/testimonials/James-M.jpg">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <span class="testimonial-name">James McCarthy</span><br>
                                <span class="testimonial-company">
                                    <b>Guardian Childcare</b>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quote-marks">
                            <span class="quote-marks">&ldquo;</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimony-text">
                            <p>Our business challenge was about how to connect with our families in a more proactive way.
                        We had no CRM, we had no formal database, we were using spreadsheets.
                        We weren't ready to invest in an off-the-shelf SAP or large-scale enterprise system.
                    <br><br>If your business is going through a period of change and you're uncertain about what
                        infrastructure to take on board&mdash;particularly from a technology point of view&mdash;<b>I can't recommend Rapid enough</b>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Second Testimony -->
                    <div class="flex-item-testimony">
                        <div class="testimony-speaker">
                            <div class="testimonial-head">
                                <img src="/images/testimonials/Darryl-H.png">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <span class="testimonial-name">Darryl Hopkins</span><br>
                                <span class="testimonial-company">
                                    <b>Torsion Homes</b>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quote-marks">
                            <span class="quote-marks">&ldquo;</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimony-text">
                            <p>Before Rapid we were using detailed Excel spreadsheets&mdash;I think a lot of people's file systems were probably their inbox.
                    Now it's compiled, it's easy to access, we can run reports on all of that data.
                    <br><br>
                                <b>It's a whole different world for us now.</b>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% include '../components/cta/knowmore.njk' %}
            </div>

        </div>
        {# End of Wrap div #}

        {% include '../components/footer.njk' %}
